<component type="desktop-application">
    <id>io.github.jalau_capstones.pacman-recreation</id>
    <name>Pacman Recreation</name>
    <summary>Classic Pac-Man arcade game with multiplayer</summary>

    <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
    <project_license>MIT</project_license>

    <description>
        <p>This is a faithful recreation of the classic Pac-Man arcade game, built as an educational project. It features the iconic maze, ghosts with distinct AI, and the pellet-chomping gameplay you know and love. The game also includes a multiplayer mode, allowing you to compete with friends.</p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Single-player mode with multiple levels</li>
            <li>Multiplayer mode for up to 5 players</li>
            <li>Faithful ghost AI implementation</li>
            <li>Score tracking and profile system</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

